<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">GlyphMate 1.0.0</h3>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">2025-10-05</div>


<p>Initial public release of GlyphMate.</p>


<h4 class="font-semibold mt-4">Added</h4>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
<li><strong>Core UI:</strong> Side-by-side font comparison panels.</li>
<li><strong>Font Support:</strong> Load and preview Google Fonts and local system fonts.</li>
<li><strong>Font Selection:</strong> Searchable grouped dropdown for all fonts.</li>
<li><strong>Live Preview:</strong> Real-time preview with adjustable font size.</li>
<li><strong>PDF Export:</strong> Professional specimen export with portrait/landscape & templates.</li>
<li><strong>Settings:</strong> Light/Dark mode, About dialog, Open Source Licenses, placeholders for legal pages.</li>
<li><strong>Windows Installer:</strong> Inno Setup installer with required C++ dependencies.</li>
</ul>
